home.title: Agent Studio
home.subtitle: A dedicated platform within the Cloudera AI ecosystem that empowers users to design, test, and deploy multi-agent workflows.
home.banner.createWorkflows.content: Start by creating a workflow assigning multiple agents, with configurations tailored to specific tasks and tools.
home.banner.createAgentsTools.content: Agents can be created as standalone entities, configured to work with tools, and reused across workflows.
home.banner.assignTasks.content: Assign tasks to tell your agents what to do.
home.banner.deployWorkflow.content: Workflows can be deployed as standalone applications in Cloudera's AI Workbench, enabling other users to interact with and benefit from them for specific tasks.
